# Slack Services

## What is a Slack Service?
Slack Services are services that either enable communication to Slack or actually consume/produce content to Slack.

## Papika
A utility which operates a kafka producer which publishes from Slack onto the topic called `papika_from_slack` and
consumes kafka data and sends it to Slack on `papika_to_slack`.

## TSARelay
Relays posts from Techie Scum App onto the Slack `#techiescumapp` channel.

## Kokona
A Slack bot which responds to user interaction.